.ft P
.fi
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.sp
See available images:
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
.ft C
glance image\-list
.ft P
.fi
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.sp
Create new image:
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
.ft C
glance image\-create \-\-name foo \-\-disk\-format=qcow2 \e
                    \-\-container\-format=bare \-\-visibility=public \e
                    \-\-file /tmp/foo.img
.ft P
.fi
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.sp
Describe a specific image:
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
